<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.4.6">
<l>miṉṉē riṭaiyār vēṭkai yaimāṟ ṟiyirun</l>
<l>teṉṉī rirumi yempālvanta teṉṟika ḻātamuṉ</l>
<l>toṉṉī rilaṅkai malaṅkavi laṅkeri yūṭṭiṉāṉ</l>
<l>naṉṉīr naṟaiyūr nāmtoḻu tumeḻu neñcamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Before those with lightning-like waists, [their] affections having been altered,</l>
<l>Can scold saying, “Why are you coming near us here coughing?”</l>
<l>Arise, [my] heart! We will worship in Naṟaiyūr, with excellent water,</l>
<l>The one who poured [down] bright fire to plague Laṅkā with ancient waters.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
